{"tid":1165931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有個佔有欲好強嘅呀媽","createTime":"2019-05-22T06:18:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T06:26:20.000Z","uid":196480,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4ae34c55bd69547b5f375b2b16a1a74c7ab7aa","tid":1165931,"uid":196480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:18:30.000Z","msg":"有個佔有欲好強嘅呀媽真係好辛苦<br />\n<br />\n1.閒時唔想你出街想你留係屋企陪佢，要出街就瘋狂畀說話你聽，話咩世界上邊冇仔女唔陪個呀媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(前提一放學就學屋企嗰啲)<br />\n2. 想約朋友食飯係不孝嘅行為，係唔痴家同爛玩<br />\n3. 有咩公眾假期，一定要陪佢，唔可以出去<br />\n4. Whatsapp 一定要秒覆，秒覆唔到就一係炸爆你，一係就即刻打電話。你以為係咩重要事？原來問你件衫好唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不能盡錄，得閒再講<br />\n利申: 絲"},{"pid":"ffdeda12004824eb38570c825b23cc9210780278","tid":1165931,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"老豆死左？"},{"pid":"54636f6b0032396b4949339799ce0c06072993a7","tid":1165931,"uid":196480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffdeda12004824eb38570c825b23cc9210780278","tid":1165931,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:22:08.000Z","msg":"老豆死左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T06:26:20.000Z","msg":"在生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊住"}]}